  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>A buffet breakfast is served each morning with freshly baked pastries, cakes and breads along with cold cuts, cheeses, yogurts and fresh fruit accompanied by delicious Italian coffee.</p>
<p>The hotel has a popular a la carte restaurant known simply as <em>Catullo. </em>It serves some of the best food on the harbour. Choose from options like wood fired pizzas and beautifully cooked fresh fish from the lake. You'll need to book a table in advance and Inghams guests receive a 10% discount on the lunch and dinner menu. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
