  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Twin Rooms</strong> have lake views and a balcony. They can sleep up to two people and have traditional décor. Facilities include air conditioning (during July and August and other periods depending on the weather), TV, safe, hairdryer and a shower.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Rooms</strong> also have lake views and a balcony but offer more space and sleep up to two people. They have a bathtub or shower. These rooms are located in the annexe. Superior Rooms sleeping up to three people are available but do not have a lake view - the extra bed is a single sofa bed. </p>
<p>Please note that only superior rooms have lift access.</p>]]></roomsDescription>
